text: Brig. Gen. Nyo Twan Awng (; also spelled Nyo Tun Aung, born Zaw Mro Thet on 4 March 1981) is the deputy leader of the United League of Arakan and the Vice Commander-in-Chief of the Arakan Army. == References == Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Burmese military people
title: Nyo Twan Awng
